            <h1 itemprop="headline">At death’s door for years, widely used SHA1 function is now dead</h1>
            <h2 itemprop="description">Algorithm underpinning Internet security falls to first-known collision attack.</h2>
            <section class="post-meta">

  
<p class="byline" itemprop="author creator" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
      <a itemprop="url" href="https://arstechnica.com/author/dan-goodin/" rel="author"><span itemprop="name">Dan Goodin</span></a>
