            <div itemprop="articleBody" class="article-content post-page">
                                    
<figure class="intro-image intro-left">
  <img src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/grave.jpg" alt="At death’s door for years, widely used SHA1 function is now dead">
      <figcaption class="caption"><div class="caption-credit"><a rel="nofollow" class="caption-link" href="http://www.geograph.org.uk/photo/934336">Bob Embleton</a></div></figcaption>  </figure>

  <aside id="social-left" class="social-left" aria-label="Read the comments or share this article">
